Description:
You come across a man who looks exhausted next to a large package, as you approach he says:

"Hello, I am from the crew of Tsnemo and I have been tasked to take this package to some adventurers in the upper ruins.

The package is very heavy and I can't carry it anymore, I am willing to pay you 800g to carry it, but this package has to be carried by one of you and will replace your accessory slot."
DescriptionAction: If you accept, you have to choose who will carry the package.
